{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Multi Payment","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"FluxStore - Universal mobile commerce Flutter app for Magento, WooCommerce and Opencart","meta_description":"Fluxstore is universal app that fully integration with the Woocommerce, Mangeto and Opencart","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"fluxstore","toc":null,"keywords":["fluxstore","flutter app","fluxstore","Magento app","Woo Commerce app","Opencart app"]},"html":"<h3 id=\"native-payment\"><a href=\"#native-payment\" aria-label=\"native payment permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Native payment</h3>\n<p>Current release supports to work with new Native Payment Paypal, Razopay and Tap. This gateway is compatible for all WooCommerce, Magento and Opencart.</p>\n<p>Please review this video for more details on how to config the payments:</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MrDq3CqRphY\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<h3 id=\"webview-multi-payment\"><a href=\"#webview-multi-payment\" aria-label=\"webview multi payment permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Webview Multi-Payment</h3>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/3b3c6/payment.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 93.3977455716586%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"payment\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/efcfb/payment.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/11053/payment.png 200w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/1b42c/payment.png 400w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/efcfb/payment.png 800w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/d25cb/payment.png 1200w,\n/static/f0de79c171aec6a1fbe1650d126cc158/3b3c6/payment.png 1242w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>The current release supports for multi payment on WooCommerce website. Once you configure it to run successfully on the website, it can run smoothly from the app. Add new payment key value and the image URL to enable it:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Payments <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"paypal\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"assets/icons/payment/paypal.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"stripe\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"assets/icons/payment/stripe.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"razorpay\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"assets/icons/payment/razorpay.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>ðŸ—³ <strong>Coding Guide</strong>: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Go the <code class=\"language-text\">lib/screens/checkout/payment.dart</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config.dart</code> to customize this list.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Please note that the multi payment gateway only availables for the WooCommerce integration, other frameworks are not supported yet.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"404-error-page\"><a href=\"#404-error-page\" aria-label=\"404 error page permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>404 error page</h3>\n<p>Once enabling the mstore-api plugin, the payment gateway may not work as the default. To fix the error when clicking Process payment, following these steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Update the Mstore API to latest version: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api/</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Copy the <code class=\"language-text\">plugins/mstore-api/templates/mstore-api-template.php</code> file to your current Wordpress template folder (example: <code class=\"language-text\">wp-content/themes/your-template-name</code>)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go back to Wordpress Admin dashboard, create a page, name it \"mstore-api\", and remember don't set any parent page for it, then set page template to \"Mstore Checkout\".</p>\n</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-payment/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Native payment Current release supports to work with new Native Payment Paypal, Razopay and Tap. This gateway is compatible for allâ€¦","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/projects/inspireui-documents/docs/content/fluxstore/multi-payment.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-payment/"}}